{"id": 3032, "genre": 1001, "title": "最近又有哪些社交媒体金句，你其实已经有点看腻了？", "description": "倒也不是说有啥毛病，只是听多了确实会审美疲劳。（题图来自：iStock ©️ cosmaa）", "record_count": 3787, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191020163228jywQz7fMkrOXle14.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-20T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 348676, "content": "我觉得", "image": "img/option/option/20191022063857zlmEJBrcv6FaGqDR.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667743}, {"id": 348678, "content": "我很好……我没事 我真的很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667912}, {"id": 348682, "content": "众生皆苦\n你也不能认输", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 348686, "content": "有一说一，确实", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257109}, {"id": 348687, "content": "虎狼之词", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596445}, {"id": 348688, "content": "XXX鸭", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373676}, {"id": 348689, "content": "太多了，基本上有二。一是使用过多，太全能了，什么都用，觉得无聊。二是滥用过多，词不表意，渐渐的没了标准", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1654422}, {"id": 348690, "content": "害！\r\n2019年下半年最心烦的字", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018591}, {"id": 349214, "content": "。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 348703, "content": "做个人吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667988}, {"id": 349215, "content": "xx除了生孩子啥都会？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1548928}, {"id": 348704, "content": "小哥哥小哥哥", "image": "img/option/option/20191022141008aCLiyS17mWXthBqx.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039287}, {"id": 348705, "content": "小姐姐小姐姐", "image": "img/option/option/2019102214112702E9ahHFeAiRKJ54.jpg", "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039287}, {"id": 348711, "content": "我40，我單身！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725165}, {"id": 348713, "content": "辛苦啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668011}, {"id": 348714, "content": "辛苦你啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668011}, {"id": 348973, "content": "吃得苦中苦方为人上人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596623}, {"id": 348721, "content": "再也不相信爱情了，我又相信爱情了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440051}, {"id": 348726, "content": "爸爸！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668059}, {"id": 348728, "content": "xxx情商好高", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668060}, {"id": 348729, "content": "对，我跟你一样也是重度抑郁症患者，白天对每个人都笑，晚上自己一个人痛哭（excuse me？真的是网络发达了什么词都能用来往身上套吗，不开心也能交抑郁症了？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370362}, {"id": 348730, "content": "太南南南南南了。麻将牌图", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607507}, {"id": 348737, "content": "一想到为人父母不用考试就觉得很可怕（原句不记得，意思肯定没错）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644689}, {"id": 348738, "content": "丢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603835}, {"id": 348746, "content": "对同性婚姻不支持不反对。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515598}, {"id": 348747, "content": "🐂🍺！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617393}, {"id": 349003, "content": "我丢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668954}, {"id": 348748, "content": "👍", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617393}, {"id": 349264, "content": "懂的人自然懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1669684}, {"id": 349010, "content": "悼念逝者时：1 一路走好 2 愿天堂没有伤痛", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246245}, {"id": 349011, "content": "存在即合理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517619}, {"id": 348756, "content": "事关大道理，几乎没有不踩雷的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461775}, {"id": 349013, "content": "卧槽，我一时想不起来，但是底下的回答每一个都赞同", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378892}, {"id": 348760, "content": "有钱人说的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484371}, {"id": 348762, "content": "读书无用论是最大的骗局。\n\n这句话本身没有什么不对的，但是现在居然被经常拿去炒作什么阶级了。\n现在的父母砸锅卖铁让孩子读书，这句话所以现在已经不算什么惊世骇俗的真理了。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668209}, {"id": 348777, "content": "土块", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553298}, {"id": 348778, "content": "一切风花雪月的神秘短句+糊得不行的日剧截图==", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668320}, {"id": 350059, "content": "万丈高楼平地起，\r\n成功还得靠自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672533}, {"id": 348784, "content": "生而为人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998568}, {"id": 348787, "content": "是你独享的moment", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506265}, {"id": 349044, "content": "“真正的爱情就该是xxxxxxxx” / “如果一个人爱你 那就会xxxxxxxxxxx”  世界上有多少人就会有多少爱一个人的方式 你可以阐述自己的恋爱观 但至少不要去误导很多还在情窦初开的懵懂阶段的人吧 这是你的经历或你看完某部电影后的直接感受 但这不是所有人的统一标准", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662713}, {"id": 348790, "content": "法院见，懂？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668383}, {"id": 352630, "content": "唯有美食和爱不可辜负", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693098}, {"id": 349051, "content": "一切的巧合(不期而遇)都是蓄谋已久。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496239}, {"id": 348556, "content": "“地狱空荡荡魔鬼在人间”，话是没什么错但是被用得太多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 251, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348557, "content": "10万+公众号们推送的每一条标题，基本就是金句排列组合", "image": null, "praise_count": 158, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348558, "content": "日剧里的台词截图，搬到社交媒体上变成了万金油真理", "image": null, "praise_count": 588, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348814, "content": "当你死去 全世界开始爱你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668453}, {"id": 348815, "content": "我对所有的所谓媒体金句都排斥，所谓的网络流行词也是，什么\"给力\"什么\"我也是醉了\"都什么和什么呀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1207577}, {"id": 348819, "content": "不着急不害怕不要脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382573}]}